I estimate that this one will start soon, tomorrow or the day after (there's an activity check for new players, you'll be kicked and you have to rejoin). Once the game starts, everyone is assigned an avatar (according to some theme) and a role. A moderator message will tell you exactly what you are. If you're in a faction with others there will also be an automatic message from your teammates to tell you that they're in league with you (and what their role is). There will also be a menu in the top bar of the screen, press that button and a short description of your role will appear.

Feel free to ask further questions. Also, some of the elementary stuff, such as Buttons & Abilities, is explained in the How To Play section (https://werewolv.es/guides/how-to-play-online-werewolf), and there are also role descriptions for *every* role you can encounter here.
